《'''自畫像'''》是現藏於[[都靈|都靈]][[都靈皇家圖書館|皇家圖書館]]的一幅紅粉筆畫，許多學者認為它是[[列奧納多·達·芬奇|列奧納多·達·芬奇]]的[[自畫像|自畫像]]。按照支持此學說者的說法，這幅畫是達文西在60歲左右繪成的。雖然並非學界同意觀點，但對公眾來說，這幅畫已經成為了達文西的典型肖像。<ref name="Zöllner">Frank Zöllner, ''Leonardo da Vinci'', Taschen (2000)</ref> 

==爭議==
關於它是達文西自畫像的說法最早出現在19世紀，理由是畫中人與[[拉斐爾|拉斐爾]]的《[[雅典學院_(畫作)|雅典學院]]》中的達文西像十分相似，且此畫的繪畫水準也符合達文西的水準。此外它和[[喬爾喬·瓦薩里|喬爾喬·瓦薩里]]的《[[藝苑名人傳|藝苑名人傳]]》第二版卷頭插畫中的達文西像也很相似。<ref name="Zöllner"/>

但此說並不為學界一致認可，<ref name=Finearts>{{cite web|last1=Scaramella|first1=A. D.|title=Artwork Analysis self Portrait in Red Chalk by Leonardo Da Vinci|url=http://www.finearts360.com/index.php/artwork-analysis-self-portrait-in-red-chalk-by-leonardo-da-vinci-308/|website=Finearts.com|publisher=Helium Inc.|accessdate=16 November 2014|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141129023331/http://www.finearts360.com/index.php/artwork-analysis-self-portrait-in-red-chalk-by-leonardo-da-vinci-308/|archivedate=2014年11月29日}}</ref><ref name=Univ>{{cite web|title=Emergency Treatment for Leonardo da Vinci’s Self-Portrait|url=http://news.universityproducts.com/?p=1693|website=news.universityproducts.com|publisher=Archival Products|accessdate=16 November 2014}}</ref> [[羅伯特·佩恩_(作家)|羅伯特·佩恩]]、<ref>{{cite book|last1=Payne|first1=Robert|title=Leonardo|date=1978|publisher=Doubleday|isbn=0385041543|pages=344|edition=1st|url=http://www.amazon.com/Leonardo-Robert-Payne/dp/0385041543|accessdate=13 November 2014|ref=Payne}}</ref> [[馬丁·坎普_(藝術史學家)|馬丁·坎普]]等人都曾表示質疑。<ref name=Larry>{{cite book|last1=Feinberg|first1=Larry J.|title=The Young Leonardo: Art and Life in Fifteenth-Century Florence|date=29 Aug 2011|publisher=Cambridge University Press|isbn=1139502743|url=http://books.google.ie/books?id=PlxPUHqGcIQC&pg=PA63&lpg=PA63&dq=leonardo+self-portrait+doubt&source=bl&ots=RWaWA9Hi6y&sig=RzpXFdu2e8GePv2C0U2G9J24mEI&hl=en&sa=X&ei=9PA7VKWcH66V7AbHwIG4Ag&redir_esc=y#v=onepage&q=leonardo%20self-portrait%20doubt&f=false|accessdate=13 November 2014}}</ref> 其反對者認為這幅畫的確是達文西在60歲左右繪製的，但不是自畫像，而是一位比他更年長的人，或許是其父皮耶羅·達文西或叔叔弗朗西斯科。<ref name=Finearts/><ref name=Livescience>{{cite web|last1=Ghose|first1=Tia|title=Vanishing da Vinci Portrait Could Be Saved by Science|url=http://www.livescience.com/46062-da-vinci-self-portrait-analyzed.html|website=LiveScience|publisher=Purch|accessdate=12 November 2014}}</ref>

